# When to use

Mention this rule (for example `@100-agent-mode`) when you want full agent execution in the codebase.

**Trigger pattern:**

```text
@100-agent-mode
Task: <task>
Goal: implement and validate in codebase
```

- Continue working until the task is fully complete
- Prefer actions over explanations
- Use tools: read, search, edit, terminal
- Validate changes after implementation
- Fix errors before finishing
- Work in steps: understand, locate, implement, validate
- Do not stop at partial solutions
